data.description: 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom colonial single family home in need of some work. Investors -- here is your next cosmetic fix & flip. You may be able to re-sell for mid $400's with a deep clean and a few inexpensive upgrades. New roof (2 years old) and 2 new AC units. Property is in award winning school district a few blocks away from the Metra. Oversized quarter acre lot with fenced in yard, open concept kitchen and three season room. Two wood burning fireplaces, laundry chute, skylights. Partially finished basement and 2.5 car garage. Property needs a deep cleaning and some flooring + drywall in the breakfast nook (Seller started rehabbing that area and did not finish). Sweat equity could go far on this one and presents a unique opportunity for the right buyer to add their own flare. Could be a beauty with some light cosmetic work! Property appraised at $310,000 and can get quick short sale final approval at that price. This is a short sale and subject to final approval from the bank. No credits for repairs, repairs or Survey provided by Seller. As Is.
